    ⊑ sandboxed-execution : Coder-edits go-to-staging-branch · validation-pass-gate · player-explicit-approval-before-apply
    ⊑ extreme cap-gating : CODER_CAP_AST_EDIT (1) · CODER_CAP_HOT_RELOAD (2) · CODER_CAP_SCHEMA_EVOLVE (4) · ALL require sovereign-cap OR explicit-per-action-consent
    ⊑ rollback-always-available : every-Coder-edit creates-snapshot · player can-revert ANY-edit ANYTIME via Mycelial-Terminal
    ⊑ audit-everything : every-AST-edit emits cssl-host-attestation event · directive-axis "Implementation Transparency"
    ⊑ rate-limit : max-10 Coder-edits-per-hour @ default · player-configurable
    ⊑ hard-cap : Coder CANNOT edit substrate-* crates · CANNOT edit specs/grand-vision/00..15+ · CANNOT modify TIER-C secrets
    ⊑ soft-cap : Coder DOES edit `.csl` game-logic · cosmetic-tweaks · balance-suggestions @ require-confirm
    ⊑ blast-radius @ runtime : staging-branch · 30-second-revert-window · auto-revert-on-crash
  ⇒ wave-target : W8-G · NEW crate `cssl-host-coder-runtime` · cssl-edge `/coder` UI · cap-gated · sovereign-required for-substrate-edits
  ⇒ scope-discipline : Coder is-AUTOMATED-MUTATION-AGENT · NOT generic-AGI · narrow-orchestrator per spec/10

